OL,3,CSouth Yorkshire Mayor will back
OL,4,Cfunding to reopen Doncaster Sheffield
OL,5,CAirport
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire Mayor Oliver Coppard
OL,8,Fhas announced that he's prepared to
OL,9,Fwrite a cheque for #160 million of
OL,10,Fpublic money to see flights return to
OL,11,FDoncaster Sheffield Airport for the
OL,12,Ffirst time since 2022.
OL,14,FThe airport was wound down in late
OL,15,F2022, with the loss of about 800 jobs,
OL,16,Fafter owners Peel Group said it was no
OL,17,Flonger financially viable.
