OL,3,CSouth Yorkshire Mayor will back
OL,4,Cfunding to reopen Doncaster Sheffield
OL,5,CAirport
OL,7,FThe government said it would provide
OL,8,F#30 million of funding to help get the
OL,9,Fairport back open, but another #160
OL,10,Fmillion is needed to get planes flying
OL,11,Fagain.
OL,13,FNow Mr Coppard said he will vote in
OL,14,Ffavour of the funding at a meeting of
OL,15,Fthe South Yorkshire Mayoral Combined
OL,16,FAuthority board on Tuesday 9 September.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV News Calendar, he
OL,19,Fsaid: "This is a massive project. It's
OL,20,Falways been a massive project.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
