OL,3,CSouth Yorkshire Mayor will back
OL,4,Cfunding to reopen Doncaster Sheffield
OL,5,CAirport
OL,7,F"The decision next week will be for
OL,8,Fall of the leaders of South Yorkshire
OL,9,Fto take together, me amongst them. As
OL,10,Fthe Mayor of South Yorkshire, I will
OL,11,Fbe backing that project because I
OL,12,Fbelieve it's a huge opportunity for
OL,13,Fthe whole of South Yorkshire."
OL,15,FOnly last week, Mr Coppard said there
OL,16,Fwere still "challenges to overcome"
OL,17,Fand couldn't confirm whether the
OL,18,Fairport would ever reopen.
