OL,7,FWhen asked about the change of heart,
OL,8,Fhe said: "We've been doing the work
OL,9,Ffor the last number of months, the
OL,10,Flast couple of years, quite frankly,
OL,11,Fto get to this stage and right up
OL,12,Funtil last week we were still doing
OL,13,Fthat work.
OL,15,F"Now I have talked to my team, I have
OL,16,Ftalked to experts in the field, and
OL,17,Fwhat they're telling me is that this
OL,18,Fis a project that we should be
OL,19,Fbacking."
