OL,5,CAirport
OL,7,FIn terms of timings, if funding is
OL,8,Fgiven the green light on Tuesday 9
OL,9,FSeptember, Mr Coppard said: "We think
OL,10,Fa fully operational airport is
OL,11,Fprobably going to happen about 2028.
OL,12,FThere'll be some things that happen
OL,13,Fsooner, some things that take a little
OL,14,Fbit longer, but we'll get there as
OL,15,Fquickly as we can for all of it."
OL,17,FSince the closure, South Yorkshire
OL,18,Fpolitical leaders and business groups
OL,19,Fhave campaigned to reopen the facility.
